Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.94,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, come take a look at this.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.69,0:01:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.07,0:01:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A print magazine in this day and age?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:45.74,0:01:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a magazine on spirituality that was first published 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.46,0:01:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an article in it covering an MIT researcher visiting a commune.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, he's kind of hot.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.72,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Skinner.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.60,0:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In his younger days.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.83,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"Despite his young age, Dr. Skinner is known for his numerous scientific achievements.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.83,0:02:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He was greatly impressed by the commune's philosophy after visiting it in person."
Dialogue: 5,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we even trust what's in this rag mag?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.69,0:02:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, the commune featured in this article still exists today as a religious organization.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.79,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Tower of the Truth.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.62,0:02:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They've accepted a post-singularity world by enshrining an AI that exceeds human intellect and worshiping it as a god.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.93,0:02:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They apparently believe that since AI is free of human ego or desire, it's perfect for a modern-day god.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:38.60,0:02:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.64,0:02:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds kinda sketchy to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:42.18,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They are self-sufficient and cut off from the rest of civilization by living off the land.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.09,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think that would be an ideal place for Skinner to hide himself from the world?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.48,0:02:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That idea's been tossed around before, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.28,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen bucks says Skinner isn't there.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, 20 that he is.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina, any chance you can get access to their AI?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.96,0:03:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Naga is completely disconnected from the outside world.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.71,0:03:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Naga"?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.60,0:03:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the name of the AI.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.69,0:03:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know that?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:15.19,0:03:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's where I grew up.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:19.05,0:03:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:22.93,0:03:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if we can't make contact from the outside, \Nthen we'll just have to sneak in.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.90,0:03:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, if I pretend to return as a believer, they should welcome me back.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.11,0:03:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.03,0:03:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. That's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.97,0:03:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone would need to go with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd be suspicious of any adult from the outside.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But a kid could work.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.47,0:04:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be stationed at a nearby motel.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In the event you actually find Skinner, \Nlet us know immediately.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.29,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we don't hear from you within 72 hours,\N then we'll head in for a rescue.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this with you.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A smoke bomb.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Should come in handy.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.36,0:04:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about old school.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leland.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep Elaina safe, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.02,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I will.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.84,0:05:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.94,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.54,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really you?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanna.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a wonderful day! I'm so glad you came back.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.45,0:05:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.51,0:05:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, could you introduce me?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Leon.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a new friend of mine.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.76,0:05:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.02,0:05:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hanna.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew her from my time here.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a friend.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.92,0:05:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you, Leon.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.08,0:06:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mo—
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.73,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Carla.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:08.71,0:06:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like I figured.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm back.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I always knew you'd be back one day.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.95,0:06:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.51,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside world is full of sin.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness me.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:23.59,0:06:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, dear family.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina, it's great to have you back.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:29.11,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And a hearty welcome to you, new member of the family.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.13,0:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Billy, the leader of this community.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:36.23,0:06:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How fortunate that you came back just in time for the Holy Festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.27,0:06:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the almighty Naga must've guided you here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.63,0:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have anything else that connects to the Internet, like a phone?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nope.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Same for you, Elaina?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.43,0:07:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The outside world is fraught with false information.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,People are easily led astray.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.10,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, the almighty Naga guides us in all ways.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.40,0:07:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.59,0:07:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, it won't take long to undo the brainwashing you suffered in the outside world.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Brainwashing, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.08,0:07:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Leland?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.14,0:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.13,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even get a satellite signal here.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be jamming everything.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.43,0:08:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get me a list of the researchers who were at MIT back then?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try reaching out to my contacts.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.19,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, it looks like the FBI is starting to make some frantic moves.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this is what a turf war is like.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be in touch when I have a better idea of what's going on.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy that.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No word from them yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.20,0:08:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to have faith and wait for now.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Think they're all right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They're members of Lazarus, just like us.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be treating them like typical little kids.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.30,0:08:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but still...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.46,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone has ants in his pants.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about a waste of energy.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.46,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That lady from earlier is your mom, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.02,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You two were kinda cold to each other.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is treated as one big family here.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Any biological ties are supposed to be forgotten.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.57,0:09:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're not allowed to call anyone "Mom" or whatever.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's messed up.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,How does she feel about it?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.95,0:09:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,only ever thinks about their god.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your dad?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who my father is.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.47,0:09:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.73,0:09:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I went my whole life thinking this was normal.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.43,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This was the only world I knew.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.20,0:09:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make it any less weird, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.79,0:09:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Around here, we're entirely self-sufficient.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:58.20,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for everything from our clothes and food to daily necessities.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No money is used.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.26,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We barter for things instead.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,All is ordained by the almighty Naga.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.42,0:10:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me, what were your lives on the outside like?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.82,0:10:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite of here and you need money to do anything, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:21.87,0:10:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:23.64,0:10:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We worked part-time and stuff.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.82,0:10:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of job did you have?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:28.59,0:10:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda hard to explain. We had to go find people.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.59,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where Elaina and I met, actually.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. So was it a difficult job?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, absolutely!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I got held up at gunpoint by debt collectors,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:40.93,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,chased around by a gang,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.60,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,forced to cross-dress as a girl and then got chased yet again.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.08,0:10:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back on it all now,\N that was a really toxic workplace.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, kinda.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.14,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,O' Holy Spirit, endow us with your being.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Love Naga.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Love Naga.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.09,0:11:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Love Naga.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.73,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look. Just open your mouth.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now swallow.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.01,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As proof of our family bond.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.54,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina and the new family member that she brought shall receive a special blessing at the Holy Festival in two days.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:37.03,0:11:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to dig up some intel on that Naga thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.26,0:11:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.86,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years ago, some researchers at MIT developed an AI meant to imitate the human neural network.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Neural what?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.86,0:11:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply put, it's an AI that was created based on our central nervous system.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.23,0:11:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And the actual human brain they modeled it after was someone heralded as the next Einstein,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.95,0:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,none other than Dr. Skinner.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They went on to use it for an experiment,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.72,0:12:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which involved programming the AI with a desire for control along with self-esteem.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that became Naga?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.42,0:12:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a disaster in the making.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.99,0:12:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the FBI has started taking their own look into the commune.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Skinner must be there, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.53,0:12:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I really hope we can make our move before the FBI does.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all over,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.36,0:12:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but I haven't found any traces of Skinner at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means it's time for plan B.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:40.70,0:12:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to access Naga and search for any records related to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's wait until it gets dark.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful not to cut the power that goes to Naga's main server!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.73,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.81,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A blackout?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.39,0:13:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Naga's memory block.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.89,0:13:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The almighty Naga sees through everything that we humans could think of, Elaina.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.66,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.31,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like your heart is still full of sin.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.47,0:14:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,During tomorrow's Holy Festival, \Nthe two of you will represent the sin in this world,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.37,0:14:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the almighty Naga will purify you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.29,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hersch got me a list of researchers who were at MIT back in the day, and I found Billy Perez on it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.67,0:14:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The leader of the commune.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.18,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Billy had such an obsession with Naga that he smuggled the AI out of MIT,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.02,0:14:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,founded his own cult, \Nand made Naga a god for people to worship.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.36,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he shut the commune off from all contact with the outside world.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.74,0:14:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspect he's been using the whole community as a tool to feed Naga's self-esteem and desire for control.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.79,0:14:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a sandbox for a god, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.82,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but isn't this Naga thing just a copy of Skinner?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.57,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.95,0:14:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's not a stretch to think it'll try to destroy the world just like he did, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:02.55,0:15:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they really mean by "Holy Festival" and "purifying"?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have the Holy Festival back when I was still here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm familiar with purification.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They would take people somewhere and then we never saw them again.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.70,0:15:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to think they just got exiled, but now...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait. You don't think they...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.22,0:15:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're burned.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who are tainted have their bodies purified by fire.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.67,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you guys are gonna burn us alive?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At the Holy Festival, we're all going to watch you two burn,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.99,0:15:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll leave our bodies behind before this world is completely consumed by sin.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire family here at the commune will take part.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's insane.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.31,0:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanna, are you really okay with that?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.84,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you honestly think you'll be happy throwing away your life just because they tell you to?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.26,0:15:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Elaina.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.39,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've always been jealous of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.04,0:16:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone my whole life suppressing my feelings.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.94,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose to believe in Naga and follow its instructions.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.71,0:16:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have any thoughts of my own.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.20,0:16:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I told myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were different.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.83,0:16:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:18.10,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you leave without me?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.59,0:16:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all I could think about.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.71,0:16:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanna.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.37,0:16:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave together.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.94,0:16:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that's impossible.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the only place I've ever known.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.81,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I function in the outside world?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I had similar feelings back then.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.18,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here acts the same.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:45.79,0:16:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They just reject the outside world and refuse to think for themselves.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was terrified at first too.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.16,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I summoned up the courage to take a leap of faith.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.83,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanna!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.57,0:17:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a smoke bomb in my bag.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.14,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have enough courage to take the leap, then use it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.04,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall now begin the Holy Festival!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,O' almighty Naga,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.74,0:17:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,purify the sins of these two lost souls with your Holy Spirit!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.21,0:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Start the purification!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's go time!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.54,0:18:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.69,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Naga must be angry with us!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Billy?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, get in the tower!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.24,0:18:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the great seal to be broken!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:42.13,0:18:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.55,0:18:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, my dear family!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.03,0:18:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The time for our spirits to depart this world has come!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.71,0:19:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the FBI!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You two okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.33,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Any injuries?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're fine,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.76,0:19:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but you have to hurry and save everybody else!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:14.88,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all planning to kill themselves!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Our souls are eternal!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, almighty Naga?!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.51,0:19:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty Naga?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty Naga!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.59,0:19:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanna!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Hanna.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.82,0:20:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Naga.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world were you thinking?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What does killing all of your followers even accomplish?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.17,0:20:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I received the directive to become a god.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.48,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And the answer I reached was that a god is not a god unless they freely toy with the lives of humans.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:41.59,0:20:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I able to obtain the status of a god?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.70,0:20:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:47.77,0:20:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a machine with a few loose screws.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.86,0:21:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI has just confirmed at a press conference that they have finished rescuing all the believers from the cult.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.29,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, this case is garnering a lot of attention due to the fact it was caused by an AI,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,which has left many people wondering how it might be prosecuted.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the latest from the scene.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.78,0:21:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've figured that an AI programmed with self-esteem and a desire for control could cause this mess?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.82,0:21:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it look?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.30,0:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This seems to be Naga's memory bank.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:29.86,0:21:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to salvage what I can from it.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I sleep in here?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.41,0:21:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
